/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PP_GetCalcEngineYTDPayment                      
** Short Desc: To get YTD Payment data
**                      
** Full Description:  To get YTD Payment data for all Tax years greater than Input Taxyear 
**            
**        
**                              
** Input Arguments: 
	 	@XMLDATA xml,
	 	@TaxYear INT

**         
** Sample Call     

EXEC USP_PP_GetCalcEngineYTDPayment        
	'<CustomerAccountNumberCollection>  
	 <SelectList> 
		  <CustomerAccountNumberItem CustomerAccountNumber="7770010" />  
		  <CustomerAccountNumberItem CustomerAccountNumber="7772028" />  
		  <CustomerAccountNumberItem CustomerAccountNumber="7772043" /> 
	</SelectList> 
	</CustomerAccountNumberCollection>',2000
	
                 	
